2020-08-22: CryptoUBI.org

2020-08-22: Remixing ideas from Wiki.P2PFoundation.net/Mode_Of_Production_Shootout
Can users control the production they need?
Can they pay for those products before they are made?
Can they pay with money or with work commitments?
Can they own land to avoid paying rent?
Can they own tools to avoid buying products?
Can they sell surplus products for profit?

